<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Oops! Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #555;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #777;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .cute-animal {
            max-width: 250px;
            max-height: 250px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>It seems the page you're looking for has wandered off.</p>
        <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/ae/aa/05/aeaa05ccd5261a7b935ff125ba66d86c.jpg" alt="Cute Dog"class="cute-animal"/>
        <p>Don't worry, it happens to the best of us. Here's a cute Dog to make you feel better.</p>
        <p><a href="/">Go back to the homepage</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>